    },
    {
        "url": "/quotes/nicholas_a_christakis_563980",
        "quote": "Social media and the Internet haven't changed our capacity for social interaction any more than the Internet has changed our ability to be in love or our basic propensity to violence, because those are such fundamental human attributes.",
