                "url": "/topics/fundamental"
            }
        ]
    },
    {
        "url": "/quotes/nicholas_a_christakis_563959",
        "quote": "One reason citizens, politicians and university donors sometimes lack confidence in the social sciences is that social scientists too often miss the chance to declare victory and move on to new frontiers.",
