    {
        "url": "/quotes/nicholas_a_christakis_563961",
        "quote": "It is time to create new social science departments that reflect the breadth and complexity of the problems we face as well as the novelty of 21st-century science. These would include departments of biosocial science, network science, neuroeconomics, behavioral genetics and computational social science.",
