                "url": "/topics/components"
            }
        ]
    },
    {
        "url": "/quotes/nicholas_a_christakis_563973",
        "quote": "We will create life from inanimate compounds, and we will find life in space. But the life that should more immediately interest us lies between these extremes, in the middle range we all inhabit between our genes and our stars.",
